progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#interactive","content":"Give a step an `onPress` handler to make it navigable. Steps without `onPress` are inert."},"661":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-28","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#disabled","content":"A disabled interactive step is muted, removed from the tab order, and cannot be activated."},"662":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-29","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#hide-step-numbers","content":"Step numbers are prepended automatically. Set `hideStepNumbers` to omit them."},"663":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-30","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#customization","content":"Step numbers (`\"N. \"`) are prepended automatically — keep them where possible, as user testing shows people recognize the component better with them. Set `hideStepNumbers` to omit them."},"664":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-31","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#customization","content":"`orientation` switches between `horizontal` (accent bar on top) and `vertical` (accent bar on the leading edge)."},"665":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-32","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#customization","content":"`currentStep` is the single source of truth for the timeline. Omit it for a not-yet-started flow where every step is `future`; pass the step count for a fully completed flow where every step is `past`."},"666":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-33","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#customization","content":"`status` is independent of timel